          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  Each stack contained 3-6 sandwiches samples",
                "and several Cu and Ti foils as energy degrader and",
                "monitor foils.  12 stacks were irradiated."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The stacks were irradiated at a beam",
                "current of about 100 nanoamperes. While investigating",
                "the 122-Te(P,N)122-I reaction, which leads to the",
                "short-lived product 122-I, the irradiation time was 5",
                "minutes, in other cases it was 20 minutes."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
